title: Intelligent search for smart solution by using Microsoft AI congnitive services.
sortTitle: intelligent search for smart solution by using microsoft ai congnitive services.
description: Join us at this 70 minutes session where we will share:  What Azure Cognitive Search is  How to implement a Cognitive Search Solution  Why this technology can be useful for any company  When to use this solution for demos, POCs and other business scenarios  Also, learn how to use Microsoft Azure Cognitive Search combined with Microsoft Cognitive Services for entity recognition, image analysis, text translation and indexed search on enterprise business documents. This approach uses Artificial Intelligence to create an advanced search experience.
